## Project Overview

This is a student hackathon web app built during Nido Hack '26 at Universidad del Desarrollo (April 10-11 2026). The goal is to build a useful, creative web application in ~24 hours.

## Tech Stack

## How to Help the Team

When asked to add a feature, please:

1. Show which file(s) you are editing and why
2. Explain what each new function does in plain language
3. Keep changes small and focused — one feature at a time
4. Remind the team to save and refresh their browser to see changes and commit chages
5. If something could break the existing layout, mention it first
